<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-8981] IndexSummaryManagerTest.testCompactionsRace intermittently timing out on trunk</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-8981</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Keep running it repeatedly w/showoutput=&quot;yes&quot; in build.xml on junit and you&apos;ll see it time out with:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;    [junit] WARN  17:02:56 Unable to cancel in-progress compactions for StandardRace.  Perhaps there is an unusually large row in progress somewhere, or the system is simply overloaded.
    [junit] WARN  17:02:56 Unable to cancel in-progress compactions for StandardRace.  Perhaps there is an unusually large row in progress somewhere, or the system is simply overloaded.
    [junit] WARN  17:02:57 Unable to cancel in-progress compactions for StandardRace.  Perhaps there is an unusually large row in progress somewhere, or the system is simply overloaded.
    [junit] WARN  17:02:57 Unable to cancel in-progress compactions for StandardRace.  Perhaps there is an unusually large row in progress somewhere, or the system is simply overloaded.
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I originally thought this was a Windows specific problem (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-8962&quot; title=&quot;Fix SSTableRewriterTest on Windows&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-8962&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-8962&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) but can reproduce on linux by just repeatedly running the test.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12782624">CASSANDRA-8981</key>
            <summary>IndexSummaryManagerTest.testCompactionsRace intermittently timing out on trunk</summary>
